OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fsunshine followed by a mostly clear
OL,7,Fnight. Cloud building in the north
OL,8,Fduring the early morning may bring a
OL,9,Fspot of rain. Remaining breezy along
OL,10,Fcoasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloudy through the morning on
OL,13,FFriday, some sunny spells through the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Cloudier again into the
OL,15,Fevening with the possibility of some
OL,16,Frain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
