OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy for much of the period with
OL,7,Fspells of rain at times, mostly
OL,8,Faffecting western hills with drier
OL,9,Fconditions further east. Temperatures
OL,10,Faround average.
